oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: First Nelson Church of Christ
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the First Nelson Church of Christ located in the Wellsville community near Vonore, located off of Reagan Hollow Road (aka Six Mile Road). The man in photo is William Carson "Bill" Willocks, Sr. (1912-1996) of Maryville.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Churches; Buildings
